------------------------------------------------------------

I do too. Have you considered donating a ticket to see A Wrinkle In Time (=
https://twitter.com/kottke/status/968556337163419648) to a child in need?=
 Have you seen Rihanna With A Pearl Earring (https://kottke.org/18/02/riha=
nna-with-a-pearl-earring) (mashups of classic art with movies and video st=
ills)? Or these amazing layout drawings from Hayao Miyazaki's Howl's Movin=
g Castle (https://kottke.org/18/03/miyazakis-layouts-for-howls-moving-cast=
le) ? Maybe these famous scenes from 2018 Oscar-nominated movies=2C as ree=
nacted by a family of young girls (https://kottke.org/18/02/famous-scenes-=
from-2018-oscar-nominated-films-recreated-by-three-young-girls) =2C is mor=
e your speed.

If history is any indication=2C the wrong movies will win (https://twitter=
=2Ecom/kottke/status/969715024385200128) =2C the right movies will find othe=
r ways to be remembered=2C and we'll have fun arguing about and overanalyz=
ing it all. Besides watching and rewatching the movies=2C that's the part=
 I like best.

