<p style=3D"margin: 0 0 15px;">I do too. Have you considered <a href=3D"ht=
tps://twitter.com/kottke/status/968556337163419648" target=3D"_blank" styl=
e=3D"color: #000000;font-weight: bold;">donating a ticket to see <em>A Wri=
